Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, you told me your past is nothing but anger and hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But no one's past is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The past, present and future\N are what holds you together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can pile hatred on hatred,\N but it's {\b0}fragile{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a rival who walked the\N road of battle with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as a {\b0}friend{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadbeat's Road of Flame:\N Jounouchi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hatred does not lead to true victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\b0}had{\b1} to lose to me...\N so you can defeat your own madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Battle City...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hatred\N gouged into me by Gozaburo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My monument of revenge...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Standing at the top\N of the Duel Tower...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I ever wanted\N was to defeat you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...title of Duel King...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The winner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!\N Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!\N I believed you'd come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take way more than {\i1}that{\i0}\N to topple Jounouchi the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least until I fight you as\N a True Duelist, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness!\N Really! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Red-Eyes stayed on the field with Yugi\N 'till the very end and won it for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not {\i1}yours{\i0} anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it back soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really thank you from the bottom\N of my heart, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you always used to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's always a chance, as long\N as you got cards in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to\N be a True Duelist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You gave me your power that moment,\N along with Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my brother lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying...!\N This has to be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ultimate, untouchable deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strongest servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was no flaw in my strategy...!\N My deck should have been\N perfect in every way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that I won and you lost.\N But there's no difference in our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be {\i1}pity{\i0}, Yugi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize your skills as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you lost to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the Monster called "Hatred"\N inside your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Monster called "Hatred"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters drawn on the cards \Nwe Duelists wield in battle aren't\N the {\i1}only{\i0} demons in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The anger in our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our worst enemies are {\i1}inside{\i0} us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when you overcome all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can you walk the road to\N becoming a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True Duelist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And for me, {\b0}that{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} is still fighting\N to find that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fighting to become a True Duelist...\N Fighting to be worthy of his Soul Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I would have lost if I didn't\N have the Red-Eyes in my hand earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The {\b0}Red-Eyes{\b1}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Flute of Dragon-Summoning\N lets you Special Summon Dragon-Types\N from your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that effect wasn't just\N limited to {\b0}your{\b1} hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It affected the ones in {\b0}my{\b1} hand as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Soul Card\N Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend lent me this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won through\N the power of my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, victory is only meaningful\N if you've won with your strength\N and your strength alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the {\i1}only{\i0} way to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll {\i1}never{\i0} need the power of a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to win this long\N because I had a rival like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Striving for a higher place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba... I know you feel the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's true...\N Rival and friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is the line\N that separates them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend's power, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need nothing\N but the future I believe in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To obtain glory\N with my {\i1}own{\i0} strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It all means {\i1}nothing{\i0} unless I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any one else's strength\N on my road of battle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But boasting is the\N privilege of the winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Battle City has ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep quiet\N and step down for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ante Rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...means this card is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The God Card...\N The Great War God Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about your loss, pal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how 'bout\N a battle for third place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say to hold up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of {\i1}joke{\i0} is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a friend's strength,\N is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! That sounds just like\N how I used to think a while back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing those words\N would piss me off to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you see...\N I changed after I met Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What you can see, but cannot see."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that after meeting Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to {\i1}defeat{\i0} Yugi\N in order to prove that friendship to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a True Duelist would!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my Dueling is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different from {\i1}you{\i0}, who thinks it's\N all over just because of one loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no mood to listen to the\N pathetic jokes of some deadbeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! I'm not gonna stand here\N and let you insult my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "how about you"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the feelings we share\N amongst friends any different than\N how you feel about Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly thought a man of your caliber\N had more of a backbone than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I was mislead by all your\N bragging and the cocky attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say anything more and\N you're going to regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel against me, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling against someone like you\N wouldn't benefit me in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a \Ncomplete waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got\N the bragging down good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter {\i1}who{\i0} it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take on any Duel challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my tenet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} what I'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "True Duelist" doesn't need\N the power of a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you just how wrong your\N ignorant way of thinking really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Right back at ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Final will feature Malik and Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment of destiny\N is fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You want to be a True Duelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Allow me to show you just how\N small your chances are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm all set here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think\N Jounouchi will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been this way\N as long as I've known him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always used to pick fights\N with guys stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chew on this, ya bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s gotten\N a lot stronger himself, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} has come this far,\N after battling against many\N formidable enemies in his Duels thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use your Dragon Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damage the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trap Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Kung-Foo Fighter Ultimator and Swordsman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he even fought on equal footing\N with Malik's dark personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sacrifice three Tributes -\N Lava Golem, Panther Warrior\N and Rocket Warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to Summon Gilford the Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gilford the Lighting's\N Special Ability activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question in my mind that\N Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s ability has\N increased in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't all that far fetched\N to say he can defeat even {\i1}Kaiba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you can, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Killing off a deadbeat like you\N will take but a few seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to show you how great\N the gap in our skill level is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gargoyle Powered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then place two cards face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My set cards are\N Deck Destruction Virus of Death\N and Shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next turn, my Deck Destruction Combo\N of Death will spread the deadly\N virus through your entire deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sweet! Nice card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gearfried has more\N Attack Points than his Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Iron Knight Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Kaiba! I see you got two\N reverse cards set on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably cards meant to\N screw with my Monsters,\N but you better hold your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment Magic\N won't work on Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! I don't get why or how,\N but Jounouchi's actually {\i1}thinking{\i0}\N for a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kind of feel like if it's Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N thinking about it, it may be\N too soon to take seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just\N went to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Keep em comin', Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gearfried! Go on and attack\N the Gargoyle Powered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put on quite the performance\N for a mere deadbeat commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Magic, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right on the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrink is a Magic Card that halves\N the Attack Power of one Monster\N on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be using this Magic Card\N on {\i1}your{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! This strategy is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment your Monster attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Trap Card, Deck Destruction Virus of Death, was activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all Dark-Attribute Monsters with\N 1500 Attack Points or more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be infected with the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including your Monsters\N on the field, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deck is about to be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Destruction Virus of Death destroys all\N Monsters on the field, in your\N hand and in your deck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with 1500 Attack Points or more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Sure-Kill Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Psycho Shocker...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilford the Lightning, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your deck contains nothing\N but weak Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, but that's rather suiting for\N a deadbeat loser like yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make all the moves you want,\N but I can already see the\N end result of this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to surrender,\N it's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's gonna surrender when\N they just got started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... This is going to be {\i1}quite{\i0}\N a tasteless Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn. I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have a single\N Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon La Jinn\N the Magical Spirit of the Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Jounouchi's field\N is wide open, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, La Jinn\N the Magical Spirit of the Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack on Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Malik, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to that virus, the only Monsters I have in my hand have low Attack Power...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Angel Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Swordsman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Angel Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Dice is a Magic Card that increases the Attack Power of a Monster based on the number rolled on the die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Because Jounouchi can't Summon Monsters with high Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's going to use the die roll to try and raise its Attack instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But La Jinn has 1800 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} doesn't roll a four or higher, he can't beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me down...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess of Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Dice rolled a four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Swordsman of Landstar's Attack Points will quadruple in strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! He really got a four!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! Just how lucky\N can Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I barely raises his Attack Points higher than his Monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your a man who\N depends on nothing but luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it! Swordsman of Landstar, attack La Jinn Magical Spirit of the Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?! A little {\i1}virus{\i0} ain't enough to take down someone as great as {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they say,\N "An idiot can't catch a cold."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Rishid from that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appeared before me that night\N in order to get Rishid out of harm way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hiding within the girl's\N mind this entire time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, big sister, as well as myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything through\N the ears of this young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you told the abominable truth\N behind the Ishtar's tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think this thing accepts me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Put that down immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SHUT UP ALREADY!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, you {\b0}bastard{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start with {\b0}your{\b1} bloodbath,\N my dear father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you kept the truth\N from me all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that it was the dark personality\N I gave birth to that murdered Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were aware, were you not, big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About this very Battle City...\N About the Pharaoh's battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Ishtar's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, about {\i1}my{\i0} destiny as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Tauk showed\N all of it to you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that, even if you were\N controlled by the desire for revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you lived on,\N that destiny could be changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart has long since\N been engulfed in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a strong human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Rishid hadn't been beside me, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let my dark side\N do as he pleases anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to dispose of him\N before he does any more wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you intend to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, take care of Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s\N Deck Destruction Virus of Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi lost his Monsters\nwith high Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Jounouchi will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's still chasing after Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me, still under the control of Malik's memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm forced to fight against Malik's dark half!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's gonna happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Blue-Eyes White Dragon VS\N Blue-Eyes White Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
